# 📈 GA4 Website Traffic Analysis

## Project Title

Optimizing Website Engagement Using GA4 Traffic Insights

## Data & Source

-   GA4 event-based website analytics\
-   Exported via GA4 interface or BigQuery

## Managerial Problem

The business lacks visibility into which channels drive high-quality traffic and where users drop off.

## Target Audience

Marketing Director, CEO, Analytics Team

## Research Questions

1.  Which channels drive the most engaged users\
2.  What pages have the highest drop-off\
3.  Which campaigns contribute most to conversions

## Expected Impact

-   Better budget allocation\
-   Improved UX\
-   Higher marketing ROI

## Methods

-   Funnel analysis\
-   Attribution modeling\
-   Segmentation\
-   Data visualization in R/Quarto